parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the subframe mount welds can cause the differential to drop from its correct position, leading to damage to the driveshaft and potentially causing loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: Sudden loud noise
feeling of something rubbing or grinding
loss of power or stalling
difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter clutch valve can cause the vehicle to hesitate or fail to accelerate, leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle hesitates or fails to accelerate
tachometer needle goes into the red zone
service engine soon light is on
error code P0741 "Torque Converter Clutch Valve Stuck Off".

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to shift, leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle fails to shift
vehicle stalls
difficulty shifting gears
hesitation or loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The leakage of a potentially toxic fluid from the rearview mirror can cause health risks to the driver and passengers, as well as damage to the vehicle's interior.
symptoms: Discoloration or obstruction of the rearview mirror with a fluid "bubble" in the glass
leakage of the fluid onto the shift lever or other interior surfaces
strong odor similar to dry cleaning fluid
potential health effects from exposure to the fluid.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The crumbling of the rubber around the windshield can cause water to seep into the vehicle, leading to damage and potential safety hazards.
symptoms: Crumbling or deteriorating rubber around the windshield
water seepage into the vehicle
potential damage to electrical systems or interior components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The engine dies without warning
the vehicle hesitates while being driven at high speeds
the vehicle stalls completely while accelerating
the engine revs high at idle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission issues can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The transmission light comes on
the vehicle vibrates abnormally through the cabin and steering wheel
the transmission hesitates or slips.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Leak due to Defective Quick Disconnect Fuel Lines and Fuel Hose Clamps
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A fuel leak can cause a fire hazard, especially if the leaked fuel comes into contact with the hot exhaust system or catalytic converter, potentially leading to a vehicle fire and posing a significant risk to the rider's safety.
symptoms: Fuel leak
fuel smell
fuel on the garage floor
fuel on the exhaust system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive brightness of xenon headlights can cause glare and blind oncoming traffic, potentially leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Oncoming drivers experience glare or blindness from the headlights
difficulty seeing the road ahead
discomfort or distraction from the intense light.
